            <p>
                Find an equation for each line represented below.
            </p>
        </intro>
        
        <knowl>
            <content>
                <p>
                    The line graphed below.
                    <!-- include two integer points so it's clear what the lines goes through like in activity 3.2.8, fractional slope fine   -->
